50|$|Tellegen {{named the}} element <b>gyrator</b> as a {{portmanteau}} of gyroscope {{and the common}} device suffix -tor (as in resistor, capacitor, transistor etc.) The -tor ending is even more suggestive in Tellegen's native Dutch where the related element transformer is called transformator. The <b>gyrator</b> {{is related to the}} gyroscope by an analogy in its behaviour.|$|E
